body:
Weird, I just did the install today, but in a Conda environment, so maybe that had something to do with it. Anyway, with 1.9.0-dev20180426 installed via native pip3, I get the following:

```
Done
TextLineDataset: 0:06:13.424233
Done
TensorSliceDataset: 0:02:17.663664
```

So, much better, but still not as fast as it ought to be...
